</option></select> <input type=submit value=Go></form><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Fri 08 Oct 2004</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="2323"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Fan Faire Ultimate Elimination Challenge</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=2323>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=2323">Mail News</a></span><br>I sure am looking forward to watching the crazy people who try this... <blockquote>New Orleans Fan Faire attendees, take the EverQuest II Ultimate Elimination Challenge! Just tell us in 300 words or less why you're THE ULTIMATE EQ II GAMER and you could be one of 30 lucky Challenge participants! Have fun, be creative, and submit your essay via email to <a href="mailto:FanFaire@soe.sony.com">FanFaire@soe.sony.com</a>. For more information, go <a href="http://everquest.station.sony.com/fanfaire/ultimate_elimination_challenge.jsp">here</a>.</blockquote><br>If you're gonna enter <a href="mailto:draknorr@vaultnetwork.com">shoot me an e-mail</a> and maybe if you get in you can be the official EQ Vault super-gamer!<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Fri 08 Oct 2004</span><br><br><br><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Thu 07 Oct 2004</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="2268"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Updates at EQ Vault</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=2268>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=2268">Mail News</a></span><br>I have changed a few basic things around the site in the past 24 hours.  I cleaned up a few of our articles and also updated our Omens of War feature list with everything we have done so far at EQ Vault.<br><br>Over the next 24 hours i'll be changing some more stuff, so if you run across any problems or want to make any suggestions just <a href="mailto:draknorr@vaultnetwork.com">e-mail me</a>.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Thu 07 Oct 2004</span><br><br><br><a name="2267"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Rowyl posts on Advanced Graphics Option Settings</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=2267>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=2267">Mail News</a></span><br>Over in the tech support forum for EQ, Rowyl posted new thread to help tweak graphic options added with the new engine.<br><br>If you're having some graphics problems, or just want to toy around, check out the whole post right <a href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=tech&message.id=73897&no_redir=true#M73897">here</a>.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Thu 07 Oct 2004</span><br><br><br><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Wed 06 Oct 2004</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="2244"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">All new Champions of Norrath: Return to Arms screenshots</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=2244>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=2244">Mail News</a></span><br>If you have a PS2 and are a fan of this series you'll surely enjoy these screenshots showing off the second Champions of Norrath game entitled "Return to Arms".<br><br><a href="screenshots/?ss=157"><img src="screenshots/thumb.php?ss=157" border=0></a> <a href="screenshots/?ss=158"><img src="screenshots/thumb.php?ss=158" border=0></a> <a href="screenshots/?ss=159"><img src="screenshots/thumb.php?ss=159" border=0></a> <a href="screenshots/?ss=160"><img src="screenshots/thumb.php?ss=160" border=0></a> <a href="screenshots/?ss=161"><img src="screenshots/thumb.php?ss=161" border=0></a><br><br>Very impressive graphics for PS2.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Wed 06 Oct 2004</span><br><br><br><a name="2238"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">SOE Announces new Game Cards</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=2238>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=2238">Mail News</a></span><br>Today SOE announced they would be creating new game cards which work for not only EverQuest, but Planetside and EQ2 as well once it launches.  Sounds like a great idea to me.<br><br>Check out the full news item right over <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/news_section/newsview.jsp?story=63762">here</a> on EQ Live.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Wed 06 Oct 2004</span><br><br><br><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Mon 04 Oct 2004</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="2188"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Ask SOE Q&A #1</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=2188>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=2188">Mail News</a></span><br>Today we have the return of one of EQ Vault's oldest features, Ask SOE!<br><br>A little over a month ago I asked people to reply to a thread on our boards with questions you would like to be sent off for SOE to answer.  These questions are directly from them!<br><br>Here's a clip:<blockquote><b>blapfrog:</b> Are there any easter eggs players may not be aware of in the game; along the lines of the smedly grafitti in qeynos, and perhaps griffons doing the macarena when charmed?<br><br><i>There are bunches of easter eggs in EverQuest. One example is in the tutorial, each NPC there is named after a member of the design team. You can also find most of the design teams corpses in a high level Gates zone. </i></blockquote><br>You can read the full article and all six questions <a href="http://eqvault.ign.com/View.php?view=Features.Detail&id=35">here</a><br><br>Remember these questions come straight from you!  If you want to get in on the action for the second set of questions - reply to <a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/message.asp?topic=76511350&replies=0">this thread</a> with your questions.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Mon 04 Oct 2004</span><br><br><br><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Sun 03 Oct 2004</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="2166"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Weekly Recap: 9/26 - 10/2</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=2166>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=2166">Mail News</a></span><br>Yeah, one day late on this, got busy IRL yesterday.<br><br>Features were slim this week.  Next week should have a few more, including one biggy.  Monday we had a new poll asking "What do you think of Omens of War?"  Check it out over on the right hand side of the page.  Wednesday we had our third <a href="http://eqvault.ign.com/View.php?view=Features.Detail&id=34&category_select_id=6">EQOA Developer Diary</a> - exclusive to EQ Vault.  Be sure to give that a look if you've ever played the PS2 version of EverQuest.<br><br>News this week was about average.  Tuesday came word of <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/dev_view.jsp?id=63626">OoW Access problems</a> and I threw up a list of completed epic 1.5s with links to stats.  Wednesday <a href="http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=2056">"SOE Worlds Magazine"</a> was announced.  Finally on Thursday a new <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/dev_view.jsp?id=63643">Halfling Hodgepodge</a> came out.<br><br>Tomorrow we should have a pretty cool feature up, so be sure to check back.  Till next time...<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Sun 03 Oct 2004</span><br><br><br><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--></center>
